findings.title: Event log issue
findings.description: Burn() and addLP() functions don’t emit events. No event emitting on fee receivers balances change.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges during a certain period, including increasing unlockTime, adding owners, changing stakingAddress and threshold value, and adding Initial LP and removing trap mode.
